<ExplanatoryNotes DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/wsi/2026/14/note/enacted" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/wsi/2026/14/note">
<Title>EXPLANATORY NOTE</Title>
<Comment>
<Para>
<Text>(This note is not part of the Order)</Text>
</Para>
</Comment>
<P>
<Text>This Order is the first commencement order made under the Local Government Finance (Wales) Act 2024 (“<Term>the Act</Term>”).</Text>
</P>
<P>
<Text>This Order brings the remaining provisions of section 18 of the Act into force on 1 April 2026. Section 18(2)(c) and (5) are already in force for the purposes specified in section 23(6) of the Act.</Text>
</P>
</ExplanatoryNotes>
